00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:28.892
The different centres within you and the centres in other people.

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:39.892
As hot or cold, may be as heavy, burning; this you just feel it. You can feel it, others can feel it,

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:48.892
children can feel it and everybody feels the same, because truth is absolute and is for everyone.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:56.892
Whether you have a different caste, community, race, religion, nationality,

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:03.892
all kinds of superficial things, which divides human beings, everyone feels the same.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:09.892
