00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:38.892
This is the second phase where you start knowing about others and knowing about yourself.

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:47.892
So you become connected with the Absolute. Absolute, means there is no question about it,

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:59.892
absolute means there is no doubt about it, absolute means it is single.

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:09.892
Today I have to tell you about what actually happens when this force called Kundalini within you

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:20.892
rises and gives you self-realization. Actually within your self what should happen?

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:29.892
Nobody tells you these things, I mean, they’ll say you are to be reborn, so you have a sort of a certificate,

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:38.892
twice born, reborn and you go about, when it’s not like that.

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:48.892
Supposing a monkey puts a sign-board on, “I am a human being”, does he become?

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:52.892
If we just say we are this, we are that, you are not.

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:59.892
For example we say we are Muslims, we are Christians, we are Hindus, we are not.

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:06.892
Because you have formed a group, you call yourself something, or something that you are not.

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:13.892
It’s just your own idea. How are you a Hindu? How are you a Christian?

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:21.892
What all these religions have said that you have to be born again.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:28.892
Every religion, Jews have in a way said it too,

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:40.892
but the problem is that we don’t do what is told to us, we just form a group.

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:45.892
Group can be made out of anything nonsensical like, I met some other people the other day

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:50.892
and they told Me our group is called as Knives and Fork.

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:54.892
I said “What’s that group?” Knives and Forks, yes very good group,

00:06:55.000 --> 00:07:02.892
so I said, “What is that?” “Because we put our knives and forks in a different way than others.”

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:09.892
I said ” But what’s the use?” “No, we form a very strong group.” “For what?”

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:12.892
“We can form a political party tomorrow.”

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:16.892
I said, “All right, go ahead with this kind of a nonsense”,

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:24.892
But it is nonsense, all this is nonsense. What is sensible is that

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:29.892
we have to become something more than what we are. We are human beings,

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:33.892
we have to become more knowledgeable, we have to become the knowledge.

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:39.892
That knowledge you cannot get in the libraries or from the books.

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:44.892
How do you grow into that knowledge is through this Kundalini awakening,

00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:49.892
through this happening that, this Kundalini rises within you

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:57.892
and pierces through your fontanel bone area giving you the real baptism and not the artificial one.

00:07:58.000 --> 00:08:05.892
The reality again. Supposing somebody doesn’t get it, all right, so he comes back on Me,

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:13.892
“Oh I never got it Mother”. Something wrong, he should get it, should get it.

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:22.892
Because we cannot give you a false certificate, you cannot give yourself a false certificate.

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:31.892
But it is very common as you see in this world, that when you listen to people who are religious,

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:39.892
you find they are horribly fanatic, funny, stupid people.

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:46.892
I mean if you want to hear about each one of them you should go to the opposite party.

00:08:47.000 --> 00:08:51.892
Like if you want to hear about Hindus go to Muslims.

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:57.892
If you want to hear about the Muslims go to Jews and

00:08:58.000 --> 00:09:04.892
if you want to hear about Jews go to say Muslims or anyone, Christians, and they’ll tell you.

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:08.892
So there’s nothing universal opinion about things.

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:15.892
It is surprising for a person who wants to see the truth in every religion,

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:21.892
he cannot understand why people belonging to religion, when God is only one,

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:31.892
why there’s a fight going on. Why this world is divided by, even religious leaders are dividing the world.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:42.892
It is very amazing. So where is this religion? And what happens to our religion?

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:54.892
When we get our self-realization, we become the Self, the Spirit and the Spirit is untarnishable.

00:09:55.000 --> 00:10:03.892
It’s untarnishable. You cannot cleanse the soap, can you?

00:10:04.000 --> 00:10:07.892
But the quality of Spirit is that it cleanses you. First is it cleanses you.

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:15.892
Just like a Mother lovingly cleanses the child who has fallen somewhere in the road

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:22.892
and cleanses the clothes and makes the child absolutely neat, tidy, clean

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:25.892
and with great admiration looks at the child;

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:35.892
in the same way the Spirit bathes you with it’s beautiful blessings so that you cleanse.

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:41.892
And the second thing it does is to give you light.

00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:48.892
Now the light doesn’t mean electrical light, it doesn’t mean the light you see inside.

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:53.892
What does this light means is your awareness itself.

00:10:54.000 --> 00:11:04.892
Your awareness itself becomes a higher awareness by which you start seeing things clear cut.

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:12.892
Like I know somebody who came to see Me before Sahaja Yoga

00:11:13.000 --> 00:11:19.892
and he met Me after say a month, he was a changed man, I could not recognize him.

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:25.892
So I said what has happened to him? He came to Me I asked him,

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:29.892
”How are you?” He said “Mother I am fine.”

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:38.892
He used to look very old and haggard and absolutely frustrated. I said “What has happened?”

00:11:39.000 --> 00:11:47.892
He said “Mother you know, when I got realisation, suddenly I felt tremendous compassion for everyone

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:55.892
and I had an enemy that was my uncle and I hated him from the bottom of my heart,

00:11:56.000 --> 00:12:02.892
and I used to think he has killed my mother, and I could not believe that he has not killed my mother,

00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:05.892
so many people told me but still with the hatred I could not get over it.

00:12:06.000 --> 00:12:10.892
I had insulted him, he had insulted me and if somebody had given me freedom with

00:12:11.000 --> 00:12:16.892
a dagger I would have gone and killed him. I hated him from the bottom of my heart.

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:21.892
And all the time I thought of killing him, doing this and all the nasty things I could think of.

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:29.892
My whole mind was pre-occupied.” “So what happened?” He said,

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:36.892
“Next day I started seeing his good points, I said no he is a very generous man.

00:12:37.000 --> 00:12:43.892
I have been nastier that he has been, suddenly I started feeling it, that feeling of love,

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:49.892
compassion and when I said uncle, I forgive you completely,

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:55.892
the blissfulness crawled upon me, that’s the first time I’ve felt the joy of my spirit.

00:12:56.000 --> 00:12:59.892
I had said this before also but I had never felt it,

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:06.892
but first time when I said this I felt it and that bliss was so great and that joy was so great

00:13:07.000 --> 00:13:09.892
I said now I must have it at any cost.

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:16.892
So next day I saw him at a race, he was a great race goer also, a very rich man.

00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:25.892
I saw him and I just embraced him. I couldn’t help it. He was surprised, he looked at me,

00:13:26.000 --> 00:13:29.892
he said come and have tea with me, and we are great friends now.”

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:36.892
So all that wrinkle, all that horrible anger and all that has gone away

00:13:37.000 --> 00:13:42.892
and this divine, serene face was showing its beauty there.

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:48.892
But he said “I have done this before, I’ve tried to forgive him, I told myself,

00:13:49.000 --> 00:13:53.892
I told many a times that he’s not killed my mother, I should not hate him.

00:13:54.000 --> 00:14:00.892
I tried to convince myself, but still I could not forgive, I didn’t have the power to forgive.

00:14:01.000 --> 00:14:05.892
But when I got my self-realization, suddenly the power came to me,

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:09.892
in such a gush. I have become powerful Mother.”

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:14.892
In the Sanskrit language it’s called the word Samarth,

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:22.892
Samarth means powerful but actually means Sama-Artha, it means equal to your meaning.

00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:28.892
Equal to your meaning, means you become your Self. Samartha.

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:33.892
When you become yourself, you become powerful to fight your weaknesses

00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:48.892
and you automatically do it without any trouble, spontaneously. Very easy it is to forgive.

00:14:49.000 --> 00:14:56.892
Not only this, so many things there are which you just do without any difficulty.

00:14:57.000 --> 00:15:07.892
It is very difficult before realization for a person to think that to part with your little bit of two P’s that you have,

00:15:08.000 --> 00:15:12.892
even that is sometimes difficult. You think ten times, calculate it, all right,

00:15:13.000 --> 00:15:19.892
if I give two P’s now how much will I get, three P’s or five P’s, all right

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:29.892
if I get three P’s no good, five P’s is all right; but after realization you just give.

00:15:30.000 --> 00:15:36.892
You just give, you like to give, you love to give, you want to enjoy the giving capacity of yourself.

00:15:37.000 --> 00:15:41.892
So far the acquiring, acquisition and also the capacity to preserve,

00:15:42.000 --> 00:15:44.892
keep everything to yourself becomes a giving capacity.

00:15:45.000 --> 00:15:53.892
And as a result of that, what you find, you are filled in.

00:15:54.000 --> 00:16:07.892
Every sort of thing, every sort of material or physical or anything that is needed to make you happy

00:16:08.000 --> 00:16:13.892
just comes down. From where, how, God alone knows because it’s only God does the job,

00:16:14.000 --> 00:16:26.892
it’s God’s work. So the power to stand up against evil, against injustice,

00:16:27.000 --> 00:16:35.892
against wrong doing just changes your priorities completely

00:16:36.000 --> 00:16:44.892
and you become a powerful personality. Like Christ when He saw the prostitute,

00:16:45.000 --> 00:16:52.892
Mary Magdalene, being stoned, He saw the disciple Mary Magdalene in her.

00:16:53.000 --> 00:16:58.892
He stood up and He said, “Those who have not sinned can throw stones at Me.”

00:16:59.000 --> 00:17:04.892
That character, that strength that stood up there,

00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:11.892
and nobody could even think of throwing stones at Him.

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:19.892
This powerful personality which is compassion, which is righteous, which is virtuous,

00:17:20.000 --> 00:17:30.892
starts shining through you. It’s not a quarrelsome dominating power in which we believe.

00:17:31.000 --> 00:17:38.892
According to us a powerful man is the one who can dominate the whole world.

00:17:39.000 --> 00:17:43.892
The power of love we have never exploited, never.

00:17:44.000 --> 00:17:51.892
All our enterprises, all our worldly affairs, political, economic, are based on hatred.

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:58.892
The power of love in it’s purest from is the most powerful thing

00:17:59.000 --> 00:18:04.892
and that is going to emancipate the whole universe. There’s no other way out.

00:18:05.000 --> 00:18:11.892
It doesn’t mean your carnal love or your nonsensical ideas of love, it’s not, it’s pure love.

00:18:12.000 --> 00:18:16.892
The pure love is that kind where the sap rises in a tree

00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:25.892
and gives nourishment to all the parts of the tree and goes back. It’s not attached.

00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:31.892
If it gets attached to one flower, the tree will die, the flower will die.

00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:39.892
So this is the power which empowers you, nourishes you, soothes you,

00:18:40.000 --> 00:18:50.892
consoles you, relaxes you and leaves you powerful.

00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:56.892
That sort of a power is to be felt if it is the experience of truth.

00:18:57.000 --> 00:19:05.892
But we have never tried to understand love in its own truth.

00:19:06.000 --> 00:19:13.892
The reason is we were not realized people. When we are blind, we are mixed up.

00:19:14.000 --> 00:19:19.892
We can’t make out one from another but when our eyes are opened out

00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:27.892
we understand the true love. And this is what people have exploited, many of them,

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:32.892
many so called gurus and these people who talk of God have exploited

00:19:33.000 --> 00:19:40.892
this side of love by teaching dirty things to people, debasing them, using their weaknesses.

00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:48.892
Saying that if you do this kind of a weakness, then you will reach God.

00:19:49.000 --> 00:20:02.892
Love that makes you a slave cannot be love and that is what it is, the love that is divine,

00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:10.892
is the love of God that starts flowing through you, you become the medium, as you call it,

00:20:11.000 --> 00:20:17.892
of that love. A powerful medium. But you know how to manoeuvre it.

00:20:18.000 --> 00:20:26.892
You know everything. It’s not blindly, I have seen some people, oh we are in love, you see going on like that, no.

00:20:27.000 --> 00:20:36.892
You know everyone. You know ins and outs of everyone and of yourself also.

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:42.892
I have seen many people coming to Me and saying, “Mother please save me from this Agnya.”

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:48.892
Now in our language it is this Agnya, but actually it means ego.

00:20:49.000 --> 00:20:54.892
You can see your ego clearly once you get realization and we say oh God what is this?

00:20:55.000 --> 00:21:01.892
That’s not me, I am not ego, oh that’s not me, I am the Self, I am the Spirit.

00:21:02.000 --> 00:21:09.892
So this separation takes place within yourself, with your own understanding that,

00:21:10.000 --> 00:21:20.892
you are not this body, this mind, this ego, this superego but you are the spirit.

00:21:21.000 --> 00:21:30.892
And the more you grow into it, a beautiful personality of a character, which is not a character,

00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:34.892
sometimes people think if you are very meek, is he compromising,

00:21:35.000 --> 00:21:39.892
such a character will never compromise, is a terrific character.

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:47.892
It would never compromise with anything that is not the truth. It cannot by temperament.

00:21:48.000 --> 00:21:52.892
But is very kind and compassionate, forgiving.

00:21:53.000 --> 00:22:01.892
Gives lots of chances because there’s that inner urge to save others, to save others,

00:22:02.000 --> 00:22:04.892
to help others, to get them to the right thing.

00:22:05.000 --> 00:22:09.892
It’s like people who are standing on the brink of a disaster,

00:22:10.000 --> 00:22:15.892
or people who are on the bank and see the people getting drowned and trying to pull them out

00:22:16.000 --> 00:22:24.892
with all their effort. But they don’t want to compromise as to jump or to leave the banks that they have got.

00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:32.892
Such a character you develop then and this character is felt by everyone.

00:22:33.000 --> 00:22:38.892
I have known many Sahaja Yogis first who came to Sahaja Yoga,

00:22:39.000 --> 00:22:45.892
their own family people were angry. Now you are following another Guru,

00:22:46.000 --> 00:22:54.892
this is another cult, this is that. But then they found out that they are giving no money, nothing,

00:22:55.000 --> 00:23:03.892
and they are flowering. In every way they are beautiful, they are becoming better and better people.

00:23:04.000 --> 00:23:10.892
Righteous and virtuous people, powerful people of great character

00:23:11.000 --> 00:23:15.892
and they are amazed you know. How do they become?

00:23:16.000 --> 00:23:23.892
And they become very intelligent, they don’t do any stupid things, they just don’t do it.

00:23:24.000 --> 00:23:29.892
Even a little child knows it’s stupid. They don’t do stupid things.

00:23:30.000 --> 00:23:39.892
They don’t do nonsensical things. They are dignified and they don’t take to cheap entertainments.

00:23:40.000 --> 00:23:49.892
The depth that you feel in the poets, in the great musicians, becomes their own nature.

00:23:50.000 --> 00:24:02.892
When they talk, when they walk, any rapport with them, you can feel the depth of their spirit.

00:24:03.000 --> 00:24:08.892
They become very knowledgeable suddenly. As I told you last time these journalists asked Me

00:24:09.000 --> 00:24:12.892
“Mother have you got all scholars?” I said “Scholars, what.”

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:17.892
“All scholars are Sahaja Yogis,” I said “No, at the most one percent may be,

00:24:18.000 --> 00:24:24.892
who have been great headaches to me, the rest of them are simple people.”

00:24:25.000 --> 00:24:32.892
Simple people are the best and this is what is true,

00:24:33.000 --> 00:24:42.892
that those who get realization start feeling the knowledge which is absolute.

00:24:43.000 --> 00:24:46.892
Seeing the knowledge, knowing the knowledge.

00:24:47.000 --> 00:24:55.892
Like if you see, say, this pillar, you just look at it, you say, oh very nicely done painted this,

00:24:56.000 --> 00:24:59.892
somebody might say it should not have been this color, that color.

00:25:00.000 --> 00:25:06.892
But a Sahaja Yogi doesn’t see this pillar as to how aesthetically it is and all that,

00:25:07.000 --> 00:25:15.892
but immediately he’ll say it’s beautiful. You’ll say why? It gives vibrations.

00:25:16.000 --> 00:25:20.892
The whole aesthetics are worked out through vibrations.

00:25:21.000 --> 00:25:29.892
All the beautiful things, as I told you last time, of the world have vibrations.

00:25:30.000 --> 00:25:34.892
Real beautiful things have vibrations. Like Mona Lisa I told you the other day,

00:25:35.000 --> 00:25:38.892
if you go and feel her vibrations, she has vibrations.

00:25:39.000 --> 00:25:50.892
Now the one who has made her has put his joy into her and she emits vibrations.

00:25:51.000 --> 00:26:02.892
And that is the thing that gives joy to you because you are at a level where you can feel those vibrations.

00:26:03.000 --> 00:26:12.892
You start feeling the physical side of yours, you understand you have a physical problem.

00:26:13.000 --> 00:26:15.892
Immediately you know you have a physical problem, you know where it is,

00:26:16.000 --> 00:26:20.892
how to correct it, how to cure it. I have seen many people who come to me,

00:26:21.000 --> 00:26:26.892
Mother cure my cancer, but they don’t come to Me before they get cancer.

00:26:27.000 --> 00:26:33.892
If they had come they would never have got it, but they had no time, at that time they had no time.

00:26:34.000 --> 00:26:41.892
But when they get cancer I have no time either. It happens always.

00:26:42.000 --> 00:26:51.892
Of course they are to be helped, cured, but why not come as a prevention to all those diseases

00:26:52.000 --> 00:27:10.892
which has no meaning. It is unnecessarily so much accepted that health is first of all.

00:27:11.000 --> 00:27:14.892
